{"tid":572302,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"劉兆佳：修憲終身主席有助支那進行元首外交　對香港影響不大","createTime":"2018-02-25T12:34:04.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-25T12:46:50.000Z","uid":79563,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"262e07e204c9fc6ab7ce4e601e1785c238fd7757","tid":572302,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-25T12:34:04.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1382508-20180225.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1382508-20180225.htm&d=mNNUuqySWYqK0AdFYghIREbWhtBCnEJYRTWbVbFBOac%3D&h=b4924f3c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1382508-20180225.htm&h=7f02bebe\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1382508-20180225.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n中共中央委員會建議取消憲法中，有關國家正、副主席不得連任兩屆的規定。<br />\n<br />\n全國港澳研究會副會長劉兆佳表示，黨、政、軍三個最高領袖中，只有國家主席有任期限制，現時的建議可以統一三個領袖的任期。<br />\n<br />\n劉兆佳說，若有人出任第三任黨總書記及軍委主席，但因為國家主席有任期限制，國家主席一職要由另一人擔任，此人在外交層面可能得不到其他外國元首信任，因此今次的修憲建議有助中國進行元首外交。<br />\n<br />\n劉兆佳認為，會影響香港的只是中共及中央政府政策，目前有關政策相當穩定和成熟，相信很難出現重大改變，因此國家主席任期變化，對香港影響不大。"},{"pid":"02049021f2acc334e45c69380d1e74b1032d013e","tid":572302,"uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-25T12:34:32.000Z","msg":"究竟當年邊撚個柒頭話要「民主回歸」？"},{"pid":"5ab5a516222daeafb9025a1ce504ee7e15c08b4e","tid":572302,"uid":1781,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-25T12:35:44.000Z","msg":"劉兆佳<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"309e1a660da3e3eadcfe6232b2146bbf3b229d66","tid":572302,"uid":41508,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-25T12:35:53.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f364718f807f0ae2ca173beff40f363dc9210725","tid":572302,"uid":683,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-25T12:39:55.000Z","msg":"今次真係對香港無咩影響<br />\n<br />\n怕係台灣要買定棺材了"},{"pid":"a13ac5dd21e27ee414da0eabcc1753f98cbaf2b2","tid":572302,"uid":91721,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-25T12:41:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>今次真係對香港無咩影響<br />\n<br />\n怕係台灣要買定棺材了</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n傻豬嚟嘅，啲軍隊係香港休整嗰陣咪順手抄你家囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f343ade9a674c1f836492000b18bf8022cd263f6","tid":572302,"uid":63669,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-25T12:45:37.000Z","msg":"香港一定死硬"},{"pid":"f056b235606b50f00e5fef33845a171a76cfbf5a","tid":572302,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f343ade9a674c1f836492000b18bf8022cd263f6","tid":572302,"uid":63669,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-25T12:45:37.000Z","msg":"香港一定死硬"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-25T12:46:50.000Z","msg":"邊個做都會死啦"}]}